Usage: set_aocv_stage_weight [-help] <stage_weight> <port_list> [-early]
                             [-input] [-late] [-output]

-help              # Prints out the command usage
<stage_weight>     # Value of stage weight (float, required)
<port_list>        # List or collection of input, output and bidi ports
                   # (string, required)
-early             # Specifies weight for early paths (bool, optional)
-input             # Specifies input weight for port (bool, optional)
-late              # Specifies weight for late paths (bool, optional)
-output            # Specifies output weight for port (bool, optional)